(sighs.  She felt like she didn't belong.  She didn't really believe in the 
Predicon codes or in any other code of arms either.  She was a Pred out for 
herself.  She saw the leader HellBeast go in the ship.)
"Well, we might be down another bot here soon if they arrest him."
(She scurried of back tot he forest in Mouse mode.  She hoped to find 
another Pred who might team up with her and hopefully it would be a 
profitable relationship.  But for now she would walk through the forest 
looking for a Maximal to fight or another Pred to talk to.)
